# Catalog Search

**Read first:** `.claude/skills/beatport-catalog-search/SKILL.md`

## API summary

`GET /api/search?q=&type=all|tracks|artists|releases|labels|charts&genre_id=&per_page=&include_artists=&top_tracks=`

- **All tab:** single `SearchCombined` call; trim sections via `applySearchLimits`
- **Tracks tab:** `collectSearchTracks` merges four sources; `per_page` controls track count
- **Genre-only browse:** tracks only (no query)
- Releases sorted newest-first; multi-track releases fetch nested tracks server-side

## Frontend helpers (app.js)

| Helper | Purpose |
|--------|---------|
| `runSearch` / `triggerSearchIfReady` | Fetch and render |
| `searchSectionWrap` | Collapsible section shell |
| `searchTrackTableHTML` | Sortable track table |
| `searchReleaseHTML` / `bindReleaseRows` | Release rows + expand |
| `expandAllSearchSections` / `collapseAllSearchSections` | Bulk section + release toggle |
| `searchArtistCardHTML` / `searchLabelCardHTML` / `searchChartCardHTML` | Card rows |

## Do not

- Add debounced search on input
- Use `order_by` on artist typed search
- Assume typed search JSON has a `results` array
- Break chevron column alignment on release rows (always reserve 18px)
